        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ مَاءِ اَلْوَادِي فَقَالَ \"إِنَّ اَلْمُسْلِمِينَ شُرَكَاءُ فِي اَلْمَاءِ وَ اَلنَّارِ وَ اَلْكَلَإِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3874 - Muhammad bin Sinan narrated from Abu Al-Hasan (as) who said: I asked him about the water of the valley.\nImam (as) said: \"Indeed, Muslims are partners in water, fire, and pasture.\""
